result.title: Bell Selects Eaton to Provide Aerial Refueling Probe for the MV-75 FLRAA
result.text: CLEVELAND--(BUSINESS WIRE)--Intelligent power management company Eaton has been selected by Bell Textron Inc., a Textron Inc. company, to design, develop and certify the aerial refueling retractable probe for the U.S. Army's MV-75 Future Long Range Assault Aircraft (FLRAA). This award marks a significant milestone in Eaton's continued collaboration with Bell and its next-generation vertical lift platform. result.text: BOSTON--(BUSINESS WIRE)--Eaton Vance California Municipal Bond Fund (NYSE American: EVM) and Eaton Vance New York Municipal Bond Fund (NYSE American: ENX) (each a Fund and, together, the Funds) announced the results of each Fund's Annual Meeting of Shareholders held on September 23, 2025.
